<html>

<head>
  <meta name="viewport"
    content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #333;
      font-size: 100%;
    }

    @media (max-width:450px) {
      body {
        font-size: 80%;
      }
    }

    h1,
    h2,
    p,
    button,
    select,
    input,
    table {
      display: block;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 450px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 4em;
      margin-top: 1.5em;
      margin-bottom: 1em;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      margin: 1em auto;
    }

    button {
      margin: 2em auto;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 2em;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #eee;
      background-color: #333;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.3em 1em;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    button:active {
      background-color: #666;
    }

    select,
    input {
      margin: 1em auto;
      font-size: 1.5em;
      font-family: inherit;
      border: 2px solid #333;
      border-radius: 2px;
      padding: 0.3em;
    }

    table {
      margin: 1em auto;
      font-size: 1.5em;
    }

    th {
      text-align: left;
      min-width: 50%
    }

    td {
      text-align: right;
      vertical-align: bottom;
    }

    td,
    th {
      border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
      padding: 0.3em 0;
    }

  </style>
  <title>Wifi Setup</title>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>Wifi Setup</h1>
  <p>
    Para que este dispositivo funcione, ele deve primeiro ser capaz de se conectar a
    a internet usando sua rede wifi.
    <br> Selecione sua rede wifi,
    digite sua senha wifi e clique em 'Conectar'.
  </p>
  <form action="/connect" method="post">
    <select name="ssid" size="5">
      {{#networks}}
      <option value="{{this}}">{{this}}</option>
      {{/networks}}
    </select>
    <input name="password" placeholder="WiFi Password" style="margin-top: 1em">
    <button id="submit">Conectar</button>
  </form>
</body>

</html>
